-- Ex-Consultant Longoria Gets Time Served in Insider Case
-- B y   B o b   V a n   V o r i s
-- 2013-07-01T20:30:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-01/ex-consultant-longoria-gets-time-served-in-insider-case.html
Mark Anthony Longoria, a former
Primary Global Research LLC consultant, was sentenced to time
served and two years’ supervised release for insider trading as
part of the U.S. government’s five-year investigation of illegal
tipping.  To contact the reporter on this story:
